woh kaun thi ? ( hindi : &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , english : who was she ? ) is a 1964 black-and-white psychological mystery film directed by raj khosla , starring sadhana shivdasani , manoj kumar and prem chopra . though the screenplay was written by dhruva chatterjee , parts were later rewritten , wherein manoj kumar took an active role . music by madan mohan was the asset of this movie . the film became a hit at the box office . its success had khosla directing sadhana in two more suspense thrillers : mera saaya ( 1966 ) and anita ( 1967 ) .